Overview   Service  Command 

Service zimbraVoice

Command Summary
ChangeUCPassword Update Zimbra's stored value of the password for unified communications.
GetUCInfo Get Unified Communications information.
GetVoiceFeatures Get Call features of a phone.
GetVoiceFolder Get Voice Folders.
GetVoiceInfo Get voice information.
GetVoiceMailPrefs Get voice mail preferences.
ModifyFromNum Modify the phone num and label.
ModifyVoiceFeatures Modify call features of a phone.
ModifyVoiceMailPin Modify the voice mail PIN.
ModifyVoiceMailPrefs Modify voice mail preferences.
ResetVoiceFeatures Reset call features of a phone.
SearchVoice Search voice messages and call logs.
UploadVoiceMail Retrieve the voice mail body from the gateway and upload(save) it as an attachment on the server.
VoiceMsgAction Perform an action on a voice message.
